statements: SELECT * FROM survey_responses WHERE survey_id = 1;
SELECT response_id, user_id, completion_time_minutes FROM survey_responses WHERE completion_time_minutes > 10;
SELECT response_id, response_timestamp FROM survey_responses WHERE demographic_category = 'Male';
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) FROM survey_responses GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT MAX(completion_time_minutes) AS max_time FROM survey_responses;
SELECT * FROM survey_responses WHERE user_id = 123 AND completion_time_minutes > 5 ORDER BY response_timestamp DESC;
SELECT response_id, survey_id, user_id FROM survey_responses WHERE demographic_category = 'Male' ORDER BY response_timestamp ASC;
SELECT response_id, survey_id, user_id, response_timestamp, completion_time_minutes FROM survey_responses ORDER BY completion_time_minutes DESC, response_timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM survey_responses WHERE completion_time_minutes BETWEEN 10 AND 20 AND survey_id = 456 ORDER BY user_id, response_timestamp DESC;
SELECT response_id, survey_id, user_id, demographic_category FROM survey_responses WHERE user_id = 789 AND demographic_category IN ('Age 18-24', 'Age 25-34') ORDER BY response_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM survey_responses WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT question_id, response_value FROM survey_responses WHERE response_timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT user_id, location FROM demographic_info WHERE income > 50000;
SELECT response_id, user_id, response_timestamp FROM survey_responses WHERE response_value = 'Yes';
SELECT gender, age FROM demographic_info WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT user_id, question_id, response_value FROM survey_responses WHERE user_id = 100 ORDER BY response_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, gender, location, income FROM demographic_info WHERE age > 30;
SELECT user_id, question_id, response_value, response_timestamp FROM survey_responses WHERE user_id = 50 AND question_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT user_id, gender, location, income FROM demographic_info WHERE gender = 'Female' AND income > 50000 ORDER BY age ASC;
SELECT user_id, question_id, COUNT(*) AS response_count FROM survey_responses GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY response_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM SurveyResponses;
SELECT user_id, response_time FROM SurveyResponses WHERE id = 1;
SELECT demographics, response_time FROM SurveyResponses WHERE user_id = 10 ORDER BY response_time DESC;
SELECT age, gender, location FROM Demographics WHERE gender = 'Male' ORDER BY age;
SELECT user_id, survey_id, completion_time FROM SurveyCompletionTimes WHERE survey_id = 3;
SELECT id, user_id, demographics FROM SurveyResponses WHERE response_time > 10 ORDER BY demographics DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, user_id, response_time FROM SurveyResponses WHERE user_id = 100 ORDER BY response_time ASC;
SELECT user_id, age, gender, location FROM Demographics WHERE gender = 'Male' GROUP BY location ORDER BY age DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT user_id, survey_id, completion_time FROM SurveyCompletionTimes WHERE completion_time < 60 ORDER BY user_id, survey_id ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, age, gender, location FROM Demographics WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 30 AND gender = 'Female' ORDER BY location ASC, age DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM survey_demographics ORDER BY survey_id DESC;
SELECT demographic_category, demographic_value FROM survey_demographics WHERE survey_id = 5;
SELECT respondent_id, response_text FROM survey_responses WHERE response_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM respondent_demographics WHERE income_range = 'High';
SELECT survey_id, completion_time_min FROM survey_completion_times ORDER BY completion_time_min ASC;
SELECT * FROM survey_demographics WHERE survey_id = 1;
SELECT response_id, survey_id, response_text FROM survey_responses WHERE respondent_id = 123;
SELECT respondent_id, age, gender FROM respondent_demographics WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT sd.demographic_category, sr.response_text FROM survey_demographics sd INNER JOIN survey_responses sr ON sd.survey_id = sr.survey_id WHERE sd.demographic_category = 'Location';

SELECT sct.survey_id, rd.gender, sct.completion_time_min FROM survey_completion_times sct JOIN respondent_demographics rd ON sct.respondent_id = rd.respondent_id WHERE sct.completion_time_min > 10 ORDER BY sct.completion_time_min DESC;
SELECT * FROM survey_responses;
SELECT survey_id, user_id, response_time FROM survey_responses;
SELECT survey_name, creation_date FROM surveys WHERE creation_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT user_id, gender FROM demographics WHERE age > 30;
SELECT survey_id, user_id, completion_date FROM survey_completion ORDER BY completion_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM survey_responses ORDER BY response_time DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT survey_name, creation_date FROM surveys WHERE creation_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT user_id, response_text FROM survey_responses WHERE response_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT survey_name, COUNT(survey_id) AS total_responses FROM surveys JOIN survey_responses ON surveys.survey_id = survey_responses.survey_id GROUP BY survey_name;
SELECT * FROM demographics WHERE gender = 'Female' AND age BETWEEN 25 AND 35 ORDER BY user_id DESC;
